org.pepstock.charba.client.commons

Class JsIntegerArrayList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.JsIntegerArrayList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Integer>, java.util.Collection<java.lang.Integer>, java.util.List<java.lang.Integer>

    public final class JsIntegerArrayList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.List<java.lang.Integer>
    An ordered collection (also known as a sequence). The user of this interface has precise control over where in the list each element is inserted.
    The user can access elements by their integer index (position in the list), and search for elements in the list.
    This implementation uses a GWT JsArray as backend to store objects (integers).
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
    See Also:
    JsArrayIntegerImpl
